{
  "texts": [
    "This bias was amplified by AI in level 2 (blue circle), but not by human participants in level 2 (orange circle; n = 50).",
    "The P values were derived using permutation tests.",
    "All significant P values remained significant after applying Benjamini-Hochberg false discovery rate correction at α = 0.05. f, Level 3 results.",
    "When interacting with the biased AI, participants became more biased over time (human-AI interaction; blue line).",
    "In contrast, no bias amplification was observed when interacting with humans (human-human interaction; orange line)."
  ]
}